{"published time": "2024-03-05T15-23-98", "images": ["https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vlk.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-2.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2.png", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3.png", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4.png", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5.png", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/6.png"], "content": "<div class=\"single-content\"><figure class=\"post-thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"323\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000000.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000000.jpg\" width=\"656\"/></figure><!-- .post-thumbnail --><p><strong>The Ministry of Defense of Ukraine has published clarification on the actions of servicemen who want to challenge the results of the Military Medical Commission (VLK).</strong></p><p>This is stated in a message on<a href=\"https://www.mil.gov.ua/news/2024/03/05/yak-oskarzhiti-visnovok-vlk-pokrokova-instrukcziya/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Site</a>Office.</p><p>If in the decision of the VLC the severity of the injury (injury), in your opinion, it is indicated incorrectly - such a conclusion can be challenged by the algorithm:</p><ul><li>Write a written appeal to the commander of a part to consider the issue of changing the severity of injury</li><li>The commander directs the fighter to the medical and expert commission (LCC)</li><li>LCC makes a decision</li></ul><div class=\"fotorama--wp\" data-auto=\"false\" data-captiontag=\"dd\" data-columns=\"0\" data-icontag=\"dt\" data-ids=\"548006,548007,548008,548009,548010,548011\" data-itemtag=\"dl\" data-link=\"file\" data-max-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-size=\"large\" data-width=\"2048\"><div class=\"gallery galleryid-547993 gallery-columns-0 gallery-size-thumbnail\" id=\"gallery-1\"><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000001.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000001.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000002.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000002.png\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000003.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000003.png\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000004.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000004.png\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000005.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000005.png\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000006.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-05T15-23-98/000006.png\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl></div></div><p>In case of loss of performance for more than 60 days-any injury is considered severe.</p><p>The severity of injuries does not belong to the powers of full -time and freelance VLK.</p><p>As reported by the Armyinform, the Ministry of Health<a href=\"https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/04/moz-pochynaye-perevirku-vijskovo-likarskyh-komisij-u-kyyevi/\">Starts checking</a>All military medical commissions in Kiev.</p></div>", "source": "https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/05/yak-oskarzhyty-vysnovok-vlk-pokrokova-instrukcziya/", "title": "How to challenge the conclusion of the VLK: step -by -step instruction", "description": "This is stated in a message on the website of the department. If in the resolution of the VLK degree ...", "author": ["Army Inform"], "categories": ["\u041d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043d\u0438"], "tags": ["\u0432\u043b\u043a", "\u041c\u0456\u043d\u0456\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043e\u0431\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0438"]}